MintRIVA libmpeg2 import
========================

This directory contains the portable decoding core from VideoLAN libmpeg2
0.5.1. MintRIVA builds only the generic C allocation, parser, IDCT, motion
compensation and slice sources. Unix frontends, output plugins and
architecture-specific assembly are intentionally omitted.

Upstream: https://code.videolan.org/videolan/libmpeg2
License: GNU GPL version 2 or later; see COPYING and the source headers.

config.h is MintRIVA-specific. It selects portable C and declares the Amiga
m68k target big-endian for both GCC and vbcc builds.
